    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a great ride without the brand-new price tag. It runs like a dream and still looks fantastic! I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, but it's time for it to find a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
