    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a purist's choice featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its distinct individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative measures, including a documented VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. While the exterior displays minor road wear, the performance envelope remains intact with sharp turn-in and a linear power band. A robust driver's car for those who prioritize mechanical health and chassis dynamics.",
