      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a pride-of-ownership machine. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment where the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, showing only light, natural creasing. All electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready; it has been serviced regularly with a documented history, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a newer set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is an honest, solid vehicle for a buyer who values a well-cared-for history and immediate road-readiness.",
