    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this 2005 Lotus Elise, a masterclass in lightweight engineering. At its heart lies the mid-mounted 1.8L 2ZZ-GE inline-four, delivering a visceral 190 hp with a sharp VVTL-i cam transition at 6,200 RPM. This example features the legendary bonded extruded aluminum tub, ensuring immense torsional rigidity and telepathic handling through its unassisted steering rack. The 6-speed close-ratio C64 manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, while the factory-spec Bilstein dampers and Eibach springs provide a focused, track-ready damping profile. Mechanically robust and free of structural modifications, this Elise represents an uncompromising analog driving experience with an exceptional power-to-weight ratio.",
